metadata.name: Don't Give Up
metadata.description:
The balance of life on Earth is destabilized. Human greed has taken its toll. However the history of evolution is that of cooperation, adaptation, communication and collective intelligence. Capitalism is only a small blip in the long arc of human history. There is a way forward for us all and it lies in working together as one humanity living symbiotically with the biosphere of Earth.  
If you are ever feeling despondent, depressed, without purpose - remember: Mother Earth needs you.  
All proceeds go directly to the Giving Block Poverty & Housing Impact Index Fund wallet. Released as CC0. For the community.
